Class LSBAlgorithm

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISteganographyAlgorithm

    public class LSBAlgorithm
extends RawLSBAlgorithm
    Hides a message using the LSB strategy. This algorithm insert a header with additional information, useful for extracting this data later.

    Jaisse Grela
